name: JellyTits (Artstyle)
description:
Would appreciate images, feedback, requests, reviews, and of course comments in the comments. Please check out my other models if you like this one.

you should look at the different versions don't just download the newest!

I recommend V3 - Epoch 8

recommended to begin prompt with " an illustration in the art-style of <lora:>, art by JellyTits "

Capable of nsfw, although V3 is currently censored.

If using other Loras should lower weights.

would appreciate tips for training artstyles since I mainly train characters.

recommended to use lower width/height and highres fix.

V1 doesn't look much like their art, but I still think it looks fine.

recommended weights 0.6 - 1
